💡 Key competencies include:

✅ Shopify Store Setup & Maintenance: Committed to ensuring the seamless operation and optimal performance of your online store.
✅ Custom App Development: Experienced in building custom apps to augment your store's functionality.
✅ Shopify Migrations: Proficient in flawlessly migrating your existing website to the Shopify platform.
✅ Custom Shopify Theme Development: Expert in creating distinctive, eye-catching themes that perfectly mirror your brand's identity.
✅ Shopify App Recommendations & Integrations: Skilled in identifying and incorporating the most beneficial apps tailored to your business requirements.
✅ Figma to Shopify: Proficient in converting your Figma designs into fully operational and responsive Shopify themes with impeccable precision, preserving your brand's visual aesthetic.
✅ Custom Shopify Themes & Sections: Master in developing unique themes and custom theme sections tailored to your brand, guaranteeing a seamless and visually captivating shopping experience.
✅ Shopify Landing Pages: Adept at designing and developing high-converting landing pages that spotlight your products, promotions, or services, and foster customer engagement.
✅ Subscription & Product Bundles: Proficient in implementing subscription-based services and product bundles to foster repeat purchases, augment average order value, and boost customer loyalty.
✅ Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO): Expert in devising strategies to amplify sales and enhance user experience.
✅ Headless Commerce Development: Offering flexible, API-driven solutions for your e-commerce platform.
